      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <ol class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">(c) See the tailorable <xref href="https://cs2.eis.af.mil/sites/10059/afcc/knowledge_center/templates/exercising_an_option.pdf"
                        scope="external"
                        format="pdf"
                        class="- topic/xref ">
