                  </ph>template.<ol class="- topic/ol ">
                     <li id="li__Toc351649491" outputclass="List 2" class="- topic/li ">
                        <p outputclass="List 2" class="- topic/p ">(8) For SMC, if the contract is a space program contract (See AFFARS <ph outputclass="AFFARS" class="- topic/ph ">
                              <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                                    format="dita"
                                    class="- topic/xref "
                                    href="PART_5302.dita">5302</xref>
                           </ph>), verify the contractor is not listed on the Contractor Responsibility Watch List (<xref href="https://insidesmc.losangeles.af.mil/sites/pk/div/pkc/internal/CRWL/default.aspx"
                                 scope="external"
                                 format="aspx"
                                 class="- topic/xref ">
                              <u class="+ topic/ph hi-d/u ">CRWL</u>
                           </xref>).  If the contractor is listed on the CRWL, the contracting officer shall not exercise the option without obtaining approval (See AFFARS MP5309.190).</p>
                     </li>
